{"tid":1744884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《國際線課金！告上聯合國！》Human Rights Foundation香港專案","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T08:31:42.000Z","uid":267038,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5f9718add066c6051066d68f43bd544d5bf1b1","tid":1744884,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位良心金主，有班手足飛到去美國搵到人權基金Human Rights Foundation合作，設立一個為期一年嘅Hong Kong Desk香港專案小組，跪求課金支持！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">官方網頁：<a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f1e40cc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\n直接捐款：<a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=179e0e73\" target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> （捐款單位係美金，用呢條link，官網右上個掣係全球一般捐款）</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Human Rights Foundation係乜水？</span></span></strong> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">網站：<a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=8ee8b09f\" target=\"_blank\">http://HRF.org</a><br />\n一個喺紐約嘅人權組織，專門對抗全球暴政。最出名嘅活動係Oslo Freedom Forum (OFF)，年年請暴政下嘅各國代表做講者，何韻詩都去過三次！經濟學人曾經講過OFF就係世界經濟論壇嘅人權版。仲有，藍絲一路話呢個就係所謂「暴徒培訓」，敵人反對的，就應該要支持！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">個Hong Kong Desk會做乜？</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 主要任務係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寫信去6個聯合國旗下嘅自由/人權委員會</span></span></strong>，迫港共中共政府向聯合國回應問題，將佢哋嘅人權侵犯大力推上國際層面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 喺各大<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際傳媒出文章繼續保持香港曝光率</span></strong></span>。個組織一定企喺雞蛋嘅一邊，寫嘅文章立場可以放心，而且唔用廣告直接借佢哋media team用op-ed形式出文，慳返啲登報錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 積極游說<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制裁人權侵犯者</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>要籌幾多？</strong></span></span><br />\n目標係19.5萬美金（約150萬港幣）<br />\n香港人登報一日都籌到幾百萬啦，個專案諗住做一年，係一年咁長㗎！仲唔快快手支持下？即去 <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=179e0e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> 直接捐俾呢個project！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仲有其他問題？</span></strong></span><br />\n睇呢度 《常見問題FAQ》 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/37snDcD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37snDcD&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=fbd75c70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37snDcD</a><br />\n<br />\n請follow<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkW