anrightsfoundation/</a><br />\nInstagram： <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhrf%3Figshid%3D1s572yng420r8&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=e9f1e46d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8</a><br />\nTwitter： @HRF（英文） @HRF_cn （中文）<br />\nTelegram： HRF或香港專案沒有tg channel，如有雷同實屬假冒，敬請report<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:15:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11.24 血債票償！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">衹投&ldquo;民主派區選聯&rdquo;盟候選人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yagiUq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyagiUq9.jpg&h=97d604f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4420cef2caabdd07e049b21c2eadec0a03915817","tid":1744884,"uid":278988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f211cc68b959fac833e89bc711ae6b0940cdc610","tid":1744884,"uid":241906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:17:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adecbfb38efc7c172e5c751691530ab57863aab","tid":1744884,"uid":267038,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:21:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">常見問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成日吹緊海牙法庭，有冇得告?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好可惜暫時冇一個海牙法庭可以處理到香港情況，無論係International Criminal Court, International Court of Justice又或者最近好多人談論嘅Permanent Court of Arbitration，都係幫唔到香港。因為一係唔係member根本入唔到，一係唔啱嗰個法庭處理嘅事。而且，北韓新彊都未排到告上去，大家都唔想香港變到嗰個程度。現階段，呢個香港專案會專注聯合國戰線同國際文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><strong>聯合國真係有用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有，但將會係漫長嘅國際線，要逐份報告呈交上去，每一個相關committee都要寫，而且格式同程序都未必一樣。聯合國收到告狀，就會請中國回應，無論中國是否回應都會記喺每年嘅人權報告入面。當侵犯人權證據確鑿，就有更多國家向中共施壓喇。<br />\n<br />\n另外，記得之前何韻詩上UN講香港嗎？敵人即刻要搵兩個藍絲上去「正視聽」，證明其實中共港共都相當緊張喺聯合國入面嘅形象同地位㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解HRF唔用自己錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢哋一直有用一部分嘅經費嚟支持香港，就算今次籌唔夠錢都會繼續做，不過就冇辦法專題咁做了⋯一年嘅大project需要額外經費支持，佢哋都應承咗俾更多嘅人力物力出嚟。手足們，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔捐俾香港本土組織做呢件事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHRF嘅經驗同國際接觸同香港組織定位唔同，而且HRF喺全球對抗暴政已經有相當知名度，亦有成功以國際法或媒體推廣手段爭取釋放政治犯。同香港本土組織路線唔同，課金當然係多多益善唔止捐一個㗎嘛！雙管齊下，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解唔係官網捐錢而要用另一個籌款平台?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n技術上同管理上用平台做專題project籌款係方便好多，官網捐款無法指定用落香港度。Funraise呢個籌款平台係非牟利機構專用，大家可以放心啲錢係絕對會去咗HRF香港專題度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我之前見過私底下籌款，而家變咗公開眾籌嘅?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前的確有班善長仁翁預先支持咗一部分，令香港專案有經費可以正式開始，不過金額未達標，希望可以借群眾力量多多支持，籌夠錢可以長期作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有冇另一個捐錢方法例如銀行入數?</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請直接聯絡HRF。任何其他渠道取得的捐款都會計算在捐款總額內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">啲錢係咪一定會用喺香港專案?</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定！HRF本身係美國註冊非牟利組織，每年都要通過審計先可以延續非牟利組織地位，所以數目要非常清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捐款可唔可以扣稅? </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHRF係美國501c3非牟利組織，可以扣美國稅。"},{"pid":"3a7ff7bfe860a9a0d1a79d7075c7d9c883be09ce","tid":1744884,"uid":25528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"推！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ef5de807d821524bf1fc2d142887331063790e","tid":1744884,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"TUI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8824d2b5163911c56294a55cad3082b80533f22","tid":1744884,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"Unsc常任否決權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近年逄關係常任國同佢地嘅proxy country 都唔會有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為世上大部分嘅事務都係堆super power嘅conflict <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09085a5fb0595f0945dfaed9d5509b2b8ba0b7ff","tid":1744884,"uid":60563,"like":0,"disl