8,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b7b71f810f8d86b028e717fccbbe705f9e806cc","tid":1744884,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"請翻譯做英文版比國際戰線手足傳出!<br />\n請翻譯做英文版比國際戰線手足傳出!<br />\n請翻譯做英文版比國際戰線手足傳出!<br />\n好重要講3次﹐麻煩將1樓嘅文字翻譯做英文!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:47:06.000Z","msg":"嚟嚟嚟 呢度英文<br />\nFAQ未譯好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s take complaints of human rights violation to a supranational forum! Hong Kong Desk of Human Rights Foundation<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers and everyone who cares about Hong Kong, here is another way to help our beloved city! The Human Rights Foundation (HRF) is now setting up a HK desk to further combat human rights violations in HK.<br />\nOfficial landing page: <a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f1e40cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\nLink to donate: <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=179e0e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a> (Currency: USD) (please use this link rather than the button on the official page - the button is for general donation and not dedicated to HK) <br />\n<br />\nHRF is a nonpartisan nonprofit&nbsp;organization that promotes and protects human rights globally, with a focus on closed societies. The proposed HK desk will: <br />\n- Bring China and HK government&rsquo;s suppression of liberties to a supranational level: File petitions and urgent appeals to 6 of the UN Human Rights&rsquo; Council Special Procedures<br />\n- Produce research reports and use media advocacy to maintain international attention on the subject<br />\n- Advocacy to hold perpetrators of human rights abuse in Hong Kong accountable<br />\n<br />\nUS$195,000 would sustain the project for an entire year. Please donate via <a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=179e0e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org</a>, and thank you for support against tyranny!<br />\n<br />\nPlease follow: <br />\nOfficial website - <a href=\"http://HRF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHRF.org&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=8ee8b09f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://HRF.org</a><br />\nHong Kong Desk - <a href=\"https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf.org%2Fprograms_posts%2Fhong-kong-desk%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=f1e40cc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf.org/programs_posts/hong-kong-desk/</a><br />\nFacebook-  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhumanrightsfoundation%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=94c47ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsfoundation/</a><br />\nInstagram- <a href=\"https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhrf%3Figshid%3D1s572yng420r8&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=e9f1e46d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hrf?igshid=1s572yng420r8</a><br />\nTwitter- @HRF and @HRF_cn<br />\nTelegram- No official Telegram channel managed by HRF"},{"pid":"1b400932e2070bda5330c055aff5f18b0926c0e6","tid":1744884,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/